seo.title: Intro
seo.description: I am the caterpillar that became a butterfly. I'm a trans woman and a software developer whose mission is to develop beautiful and functional web applications. If you'd like, we can get to know each other better.

headline: I am the caterpillar that became a butterfly

body3: and software developer, with the mission to produce beautiful and functional web applications. If you like, we can get to know each other better.
